  "page_help": "Usizo neVotre Ezomvumelwano",
  "help_system_title": "📋 Incazelo Yohlelo",
  "help_system_desc1": "I-FastWrite iyithuluzi elisikhundleni sokukhiphayo idatha yokugxile amadokumente (amainvoice, izitambuliso, vouchers) usebenzisa ubuchakubuchansi bakomoya (AI). Isebenza kuphela okomputeri wakho — idatha yakho ayiphakanyiswa komunye, kuhlanganisa umlawuli wenkundla.",
  "help_system_desc2": "Okwenza: Ulokeleza iPDF eneinvoice esinye noma eziningi. Uhlelo lukugxila luhlobonga inzira ngayinye, lubonela omnike, lufune amalibhele akulungile futhi lokuphucula idatha osuchile (inombolo ye-invoice, usuku, izimali, izicatshulwa zemuva, njl.). Ekugcineni, akhiphule imipu kunama-CSV noma i-Excel.",
  "help_workflow_title": "🔄 Umjikelezo Wesistimu — Inzira Emanyeni",
  "help_step1_title": "Setha Okhiye be-API",
  "help_step1_desc": "Ya ku-Okuseteliswe → Okhiye be-API futhi faka okhiye wakho we-AI (isib. Google Gemini). Lokhu kuyinzalo — inkambi ayibhaleza okhiye wayo. Ibahala yenzwa qonde ku-akawunti yakho ye-AI.",
  "help_step2_title": "Lokela Amadokumente",
  "help_step2_desc": "Ya ku-Lokela Nokuphucula. Tholela noma khetha ifayela le-PDF (kuze kufike ku-200 amainvoice ngofayela) futhi chwayela \"Bhalisa Amadokumente\". Uhlelo luzohunywa ngokuzenzakalelayo amainvoice enye nemenye kanye nabaningi.",
  "help_step3_title": "Dala Amalibhele",
  "help_step3_desc": "Kusuka ku-isipaji samadokumente, khetha amadokumente esinye noma aningi futhi chwayela \"Amalibhele\". Uzokuthathwa kusipaji esikhetheke lapho ubona invoice yangempela kumhlangano wasekhohlo futhi ifomu lelibhele kumhlangano wasokudla. Shuluza izinsimu ozifisa ukuphucula (isib. inombolo ye-invoice, usuku, okuwonke, i-VAT) kanye nezicatshulwa zemuva. Njenjenhlobo, dala libhele kusuka ku-isipaji amalalibhele → + Libhele Elisha.",
  "help_step4_title": "Ikhokhe Yedatha (Isolwandle)",
  "help_step4_desc": "Kusuka ku-isipaji samadokumente, khetha amadokumente futhi chwayela \"Isolwandle\". Uhlele lusebenzisa i-AI ukuphucula idatha kusekelwe likheli ledokumente. Iziphumo zibonakala ku-tafula lamadokumente.",
  "help_step5_title": "Hlola Nokuvuma",
  "help_step5_desc": "Kusuka ku-isipaji samadokumente, khetha amadokumente futhi chwayela \"Vuma\". Ubona invoice kumhlangano wasekhohlo kanye nedatha yokukhiphayo kumhlangano wasokudla. Coleza izimangalo nokupusha \"Vuma Invoice\". Ukusakaza komangalo kukhisha indawo efanele kwi-invoice njengoba udubula emabulweni.",
  "help_step6_title": "Khuphula Ifayela",
  "help_step6_desc": "Ngemuva kokuvuma amadokumente, buya ku-isipaji samadokumente. Khetha amadokumente avunyelwe futhi chwayela \"CSV\", \"XLSX\" noma \"Line Items XLSX\" ukuze ukhuphule. Uma awekho okukhethelwe, wonke amadokumente avunyelwe akhiphulwa.",
  "help_tip_title": "💡 Inombolo",
  "help_tip_text": "Umjikelezo okulungile ngu: Lokela → Amalibhele → Isolwandle → Vuma → Khuphula. Kuqala dala amalibhele ngohlobo ngalunye lwe-invoice (isib. DEI, COSMOTE, VODAFONE) ngemuva kweqa kukhokhe okuningi. Uma sengudale libhele, uhlelo luzogxongelela ngokuzenzakalelayo amainvoice oshi omnike.",
